                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">
                            How much do custom shutters cost?
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">
                        Pricing varies based on window size, material choice, and customization options. During your free consultation, we provide detailed quotes with transparent pricing. We offer solutions for various budgets while maintaining our commitment to quality craftsmanship.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">
                            What warranty do you provide?
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">
                        We stand behind our work with comprehensive warranties covering both materials and installation. Specific terms vary by product, but we ensure you're protected with industry-leading coverage that reflects our confidence in quality craftsmanship.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">
                            How do I clean and maintain my shutters?
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">
                        Shutters require minimal maintenance. Regular dusting with a microfiber cloth or vacuum brush attachment keeps them looking fresh. For deeper cleaning, use mild soap and water on a damp cloth. Avoid harsh chemicals that could damage the finish.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">
                            Can shutters help with energy efficiency?
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">
                        Absolutely! Properly installed shutters create an additional barrier against heat transfer, potentially reducing cooling and heating costs. The adjustable louvers allow precise light and airflow control, helping maintain comfortable indoor temperatures year-round.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">
                            Can motorized shades connect to my existing smart home system?
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">
