                    </p>
                </li>
                <li class="cs-faq-item">
                    <button class="cs-button">
                        <span class="cs-button-text">
                            How do I schedule a consultation?
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <p class="cs-item-p">
                        Simply call us or fill out our online form to schedule your in-home consultation. We'll arrange a convenient time to visit your property in Sugar Hill, Suwanee, Johns Creek, Duluth, Lawrenceville, or Alpharetta and surrounding Atlanta Metro areas.
                    </p>
                </li>
            </ul>
